sée Rodin, the Eiffel Tower, and Champ de Mars.\n\n*   **Cler Hotel**\n    *   **Neighborhood:** 7th Arrondissement (Rue Cler, near Eiffel Tower)\n    *   **Approximate Price Per Night:** 3-star, offering budget-friendly rates. Prices vary, but generally more affordable than 4 or 5-star options, likely starting from ~$199+.\n    *   **Closest Activities:** A short stroll from the Eiffel Tower, Champs de Mars, and close to Les Invalides (Musée Rodin is also nearby). Offers a comfortable stay with a great location.\n\n**3. For Historic Charm and Artistic Vibe (Le Marais):**\n\n*   **Hôtel du Petit Moulin, Haute Couture hotel by Lacroix**\n    *   **Neighborhood:** 3rd Arrondissement (Le Marais)\n    *   **Approximate Price Per Night:** 4-star boutique, prices vary but expect mid-range to higher.\n    *   **Closest Activities:** Tucked away in the Marais, it offers easy access to the Marché des Enfants Rouges and Musée Carnavalet. Its central location also provides good access to the Atelier des Lumières.\n\n*   **Hôtel de Roubaix**\n    *   **Neighborhood:** 3rd Arrondissement (Le Marais)\n    *   **Approximate Price Per Night:** 3-star, good value option, likely starting from ~$199+.\n    *   **Closest Activities:** Located in the 3rd arrondissement, it's a solid choice for exploring Le Marais, including Marché des Enfants Rouges and Musée Carnavalet. Close to metro stations for wider city access.\n\n**4. For Bohemian Atmosphere and City Views (Montmartre):**\n\n*   **Terrass'' Hotel**\n    *   **Neighborhood:** 18th Arrondissement (Montmartre)\n    *   **Approximate Price Per Night:** 4-star, starting from ~$298.73.\n    *   **Closest Activities:** Set in the heart of Montmartre, it provides excellent access to the Sacré-Cœur Basilica and exploring the charming Montmartre neighborhood. Some rooms offer views of Parisian landmarks, including the Eiffel Tower.\n\n*   **Hôtel des Arts Montmartre**\n    *   **Neighborhood:** 18th Arrondissement (Montmartre)\n    *   **Approximate Price Per Night:** 3-star, good value option, prices vary.\n    *   **Closest Activities:** Located in the center of the Montmartre district, just a 9-minute walk from the Sacré-Cœur Basilica. Ideal for immersing yourself in the artistic ambiance of Montmartre.\n\nThe average price for a hotel in Paris has been around $508/night recently, with 3-star hotels averaging $199/night, 4-star at $220/night, and 5-star at $727/night. Prices can vary significantly based on the season and how far in advance you book."}],"role":"model"},"finish_reason":"STOP","grounding_metadata":{"grounding_chunks":[{"web":{"title":"expedia.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGfocAUI6sxwcrOA3S0IDbIu3qKevGPt8oJsI4WW4QxICMyW5rMSGASNkAZcbsDUtGnuupjrHvGh7Aa-k7u6_X6dk39K8W6YxIesxhy-dSzNgmx3SjP5P-xGcLIpHo_DWnyCA5evq5WhowPvUwyOnLYD7yTBcctbtZ0AAvX5UtVLvbnnoSPfJAQ95rJmNOr"}},{"web":{"title":"hotelscombined.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFoZMMh9-TiEilaiLWxG0yNGGaH5Hc3mtGBgAgUGsiR4SNRq6hqzkVzrGwRUfPkyqahIkI6HQGaeIHmyS8U17EUCP_cLAnXwNVI_JiJmxjxgej2B3oWVdX557nzku63JSwda5oRwAaVN6A="}},{"web":{"title":"parisdiscoveryguide.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGvmW4y6TsgPTNtw2fwKirOtrSHXBTfHfEGdwol4nkCKx1AH8WQhc5V-xwvBSwn5VYJnuuEPc2DsgL28P7T5ubZb6yPmsD-CsLzK8ukd12yRdA7MGYZCUzBDvC68NhH-Hrh8ILDbFaWeYS4d5AKywdABzlPudAXIuu0iVau"}},{"web":{"title":"booking.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG9xO3bs-chU2UNq9nE87_XN0qu8oEv3Obl1e7ePrV6cXHRj5TJ1pwmlBtPuyPLN7eQ95A47_MIscQ5axr5ccSRK665B-SP-8wJYwh4PWXjBvmKoraeGT0RKgd-vq76SFSB8JYrWis1C9YHzX0UlOXClma5Tws="}},{"web":{"title":"agoda.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG61t9q-FQEdOP33p2nwHh3drY5bgeRbDgu8YyXnLyjyPfuSTRcbVZNI_W2rnW3x3c2TZvyxZYyLXCc40BkUChL2P7ojg416nfvOy0brWprE5vxnHrecjySD9DagVuGcLkGqmW2IrpH_Y0siwsXx9n-_pGQcnU7Oq0HIvmXTg=="}}